*eclass-helper-svn-0.02a (31 Jul 2005)

  31 Jul 2005; Mario Tanev <mtanev@csua.berkeley.edu>  eclass-helper-svn-0.02a.ebuild files/digest-eclass-helper-svn-0.02a
  Create version to not import svn, since we don't need it, and not all people have subversion +python

*eclass-helper-svn-0.02 (30 Jul 2005)

  30 Jul 2005; Mario Tanev <mtanev@csua.berkeley.edu>  eclass-helper-svn-0.02.ebuild files/digest-eclass-helper-svn-0.02
  New version which handles non-recursive->recursive switches for folders in the same kludgy way as the previous eclass.
  Plus a bugfix (ktorrent, amarok, etc.)

